---
import SecondaryPageLayout from '../../layouts/SecondaryPageLayout.astro';
---
<SecondaryPageLayout
  title="Partner with Us | Team Respawn"
  description="Partner with Team Respawn to reach the RTS gaming community through content, tools, and sponsorships."
  keywords="Team Respawn, partner, sponsorship, brand, RTS gaming, Halo Wars 2"
  canonical="https://www.teamrespawn.net/partner"
  ogTitle="Partner with Us | Team Respawn"
  ogDescription="Partner with Team Respawn to reach the RTS gaming community through content, tools, and sponsorships."
  ogImage="https://www.teamrespawn.net/content/Banner.jpg"
>
  <main id="main-content" class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mt-8" aria-label="Partner with Team Respawn">
    <article class="bg-gray-800/60 border border-gray-700/60 rounded-xl p-6 sm:p-8 lg:p-10">
      <header class="mb-8">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-extrabold mb-4 text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-pink-400">
          Partner with Us
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg">
          Reach a dedicated audience of RTS gamers through a brand that the community trusts.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-purple-300">Our Audience</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Team Respawn's audience is made up of passionate RTS players across Halo Wars 2, Age of Empires II, Age of Empires IV, and Age of Mythology. They're engaged, loyal, and actively seeking tools and resources to improve their game.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-6">
            <div class="bg-gray-800/60 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-700/60 hover:border-purple-500/40 transition-colors duration-300 text-center">
              <p class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-pink-400 mb-1">67K+</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">YouTube subscribers</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-800/60 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-700/60 hover:border-purple-500/40 transition-colors duration-300 text-center">
              <p class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-pink-400 mb-1">23M+</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Lifetime channel views</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-gray-800/60 p-4 rounded-lg border border-gray-700/60 hover:border-purple-500/40 transition-colors duration-300 text-center">
              <p class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-400 to-pink-400 mb-1">2017</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400">Year established</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-purple-300">Partnership Opportunities</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 space-y-2 text-gray-300 ml-4">
            <li>Sponsored video content and integrations</li>
            <li>Website banner and sidebar placements</li>
            <li>Discord bot mentions and tool integrations</li>
            <li>Social media promotions</li>
            <li>Custom community campaigns</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-8 not-prose">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-2 text-purple-300">Brands We've Worked With</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-400 text-base mb-6">A selection of partners and brands we've collaborated with over the years.</p>
          <div class="brand-carousel-outer" aria-label="Past brand partners" role="region">
            <div class="brand-track" aria-hidden="true">
              {[
                { name: 'Stardock',           src: '/content/brands/stardock.png',           invert: false, large: false },
                { name: "World's Edge",        src: '/content/brands/worlds-edge.png',         invert: false, large: false },
                { name: 'Halo Studios',        src: '/content/brands/halo-studios.png',        invert: true,  large: true  },
                { name: 'THQ Nordic',          src: '/content/brands/thq-nordic.png',          invert: false, large: true  },
                { name: 'Relic Entertainment', src: '/content/brands/relic-entertainment.png', invert: false, large: true  },
                { name: 'Pentapeak Studios',   src: '/content/brands/pentapeak-studios.svg',   invert: false, large: false },
                { name: 'Stardock',           src: '/content/brands/stardock.png',           invert: false, large: false },
                { name: "World's Edge",        src: '/content/brands/worlds-edge.png',         invert: false, large: false },
                { name: 'Halo Studios',        src: '/content/brands/halo-studios.png',        invert: true,  large: true  },
                { name: 'THQ Nordic',          src: '/content/brands/thq-nordic.png',          invert: false, large: true  },
                { name: 'Relic Entertainment', src: '/content/brands/relic-entertainment.png', invert: false, large: true  },
                { name: 'Pentapeak Studios',   src: '/content/brands/pentapeak-studios.svg',   invert: false, large: false },
              ].map((brand) => (
                <div class="brand-tile">
                  <img
                    src={brand.src}
                    alt={brand.name}
                    class={`brand-tile-img${brand.invert ? ' brand-tile-img--invert' : ''}${brand.large ? ' brand-tile-img--large' : ''}`}
                    loading="lazy"
                  />
                </div>
              ))}
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-0">
          <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-purple-300">Get in Touch</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Interested in working with us? Reach out and we'll get back to you with more details on rates, availability, and what a partnership could look like.
          </p>
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-900/30 to-pink-900/30 rounded-xl p-6 border border-purple-500/30">
            <p class="text-gray-300 mb-0">
              Contact us at <span class="text-purple-300 font-semibold">TeamRespawn@proton.me</span> or reach out via our social channels.
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
</SecondaryPageLayout>

<style>
  @keyframes scroll-brands {
    from { transform: translateX(0); }
    to   { transform: translateX(-50%); }
  }

  .brand-carousel-outer {
    overflow: hidden;
    mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 0%, black 8%, black 92%, transparent 100%);
    -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 0%, black 8%, black 92%, transparent 100%);
  }

  .brand-track {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    width: max-content;
    animation: scroll-brands 28s linear infinite;
  }

  .brand-track:hover {
    animation-play-state: paused;
  }

  .brand-tile {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    width: 180px;
    height: 80px;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.04);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s;
  }

  .brand-tile:hover {
    background: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.08);
    border-color: rgba(168, 85, 247, 0.3);
  }

  .brand-tile-img {
    max-width: 100%;
    max-height: 100%;
    width: auto;
    height: auto;
    object-fit: contain;
    opacity: 0.8;
    transition: opacity 0.2s;
  }

  .brand-tile-img--invert {
    filter: brightness(0) invert(1);
  }

  .brand-tile-img--large {
    max-width: 90%;
    max-height: 90%;
    transform: scale(2.0);
  }

  .brand-tile:hover .brand-tile-img {
    opacity: 1;
  }
</style>
